OOC: This is rAuq, I'm posting from Jer's house

::Astroblast::
Astroblast lands at the base. Motormaster is just off in the distance.
"Speedbreaker help Stratus, a new bot, to clear my cargo bay of the debri
Motormaster wanted up to take to base." Astroblast notices Killfest for the
first time, "Greetings, Killfest," he says with surprise, "Why are you
here? If you are looking for Motormaster he should arrive in a few
moments." Astroblast opens his hatch and awaits the unloading.
